embed -title "вқ– бҙ„КңбҙҖКҖбҙҖбҙ„бҙӣбҙҮКҖ sбҙӣбҙҖбҙӣбҙңs вқ–" -color #b19cd9 -thumb "{{image}}" {{c=character()}}{{lvl=c.levels.total_level}}{{pb=c.stats.prof_bonus}}{{mod=max([c.stats.get_mod('intelligence'), c.stats.get_mod('wisdom'), c.stats.get_mod('charisma')])}}{{req=[0,3,8,15,24,35,48,63,80,99,120,143,170,197,226,257,290,325,362,401,999][lvl] if lvl<21 else 999}}{{ms=c.get_cc('Milestone') if c.cc_exists('Milestone') else 0}} -desc "**{{name}}** | Level {{lvl}}
{{'**[ вӢҶ КҹбҙҮбҙ бҙҮКҹ бҙңбҙҳ бҙҖбҙ бҙҖЙӘКҹбҙҖКҷКҹбҙҮ! вӢҶ ]**' if ms>=req else ''}}" -f "вқ– бҙ„бҙҸбҙҚКҷбҙҖбҙӣ & бҙ…бҙҮТ“бҙҮЙҙsбҙҮs вқ–|**AC:** {{c.ac}}  |  **HP:** {{c.hp}}/{{c.max_hp}}
**Initiative:** {{'%+d'%c.stats.get_mod('dexterity')}}  |  **Speed:** 30 ft.  |  **PB:** {{'%+d'%pb}}" {{out=[]}}{{tr=['Bardic Inspiration','Luck Points','Heroic Inspiration','Hit Dice','Milestone','Work Week']}}{{_=[out.append(f'-f "вҹЎ {k}|{c.get_cc(k)} / {req}|inline"') if k=='Milestone' else out.append(f'-f "вҹЎ {k}|{c.get_cc(k)}|inline"') if k=='Work Week' else out.append(f'-f "вҹЎ {k}|'+(f"{c.get_cc(k)} / {c.get_cc_max(k)}" if c.get_cc_max(k)>0 else str(c.get_cc(k)))+'|inline"') if k=='Hit Dice' else out.append(f'-f "вҹЎ {k}|'+('вңҰ'*c.get_cc(k)+'вң§'*(c.get_cc_max(k)-c.get_cc(k)) if 0<c.get_cc_max(k)<=6 else (f"{c.get_cc(k)} / {c.get_cc_max(k)}" if c.get_cc_max(k)>6 else str(c.get_cc(k))))+'|inline"') for k in tr if c.cc_exists(k)]}}{{_=[out.append(f'-f "вҹЎ {cc.name}|'+('вңҰ'*c.get_cc(cc.name)+'вң§'*(c.get_cc_max(cc.name)-c.get_cc(cc.name)) if 0<c.get_cc_max(cc.name)<=6 else (f"{c.get_cc(cc.name)} / {c.get_cc_max(cc.name)}" if c.get_cc_max(cc.name)>6 else str(c.get_cc(cc.name))))+'|inline"') for cc in c.consumables if cc.name not in tr]}}{{cc_text=' '.join(out)}}{{sb=[s.name for s in c.spellbook.spells]}}{{has_spells=len(sb)>0}}{{n=len(sb)}}{{rz=(n//2)+(1 if n%2>0 else 0) if n>0 else 1}}{{cz=15 if rz>15 else rz}}{{sc=[sb[i:i+cz] for i in range(0,n,cz)] if n>0 else []}}{{sp_f=[]}}{{_=[sp_f.append('-f "'+('вқ– бҙӢЙҙбҙҸбҙЎЙҙ sбҙҳбҙҮКҹКҹs' if i==0 else '_ _')+'|'+('\n'.join(['вӢҶ '+name for name in chunk]))+'|inline"') for i,chunk in enumerate(sc)] if has_spells else []}}{{sl=[f"**L{i}:** "+'вңҰ'*c.spellbook.get_slots(i)+'вң§'*(c.spellbook.get_max_slots(i)-c.spellbook.get_slots(i)) for i in range(1, 10) if c.spellbook.get_max_slots(i)>0]}}{{magic_text=f'-f "_ _|_ _" -f "вқ– бҙҚбҙҖЙўЙӘбҙ„ & sКҹбҙҸбҙӣs вқ–|**DC:** {8+pb+mod}  |  **Atk:** {pb+mod:+d}\n'+ ('\n'.join(sl) if sl else '*No Spell Slots*') + '|inline" ' + ' '.join(sp_f) if has_spells else ''}}{{at=c.get_cvar('attune')}}{{at_text=f'-f "вқ– бҙҖбҙӣбҙӣбҙңЙҙбҙҮбҙҚбҙҮЙҙбҙӣ|{at}"' if at else ''}} {{cc_text}} {{at_text}} {{magic_text}}
